title: Hour 3 - Too Early to Tank, Rick Stroud
itunes:title: Hour 3 - Too Early to Tank, Rick Stroud
description:
Dan talks about struggling teams in all sports and when it's time to start tanking for draft picks. And Tampa Bay Buccaneers insider Rick Stroud weighs in on the poorly performing squad.
